    dc:description "Figure 8. Prey items identified from stomach contents of P. cleofasensis A Pycnoselus surinamensis B crickets of the family Rhaphidophoridae C beetles of the genus Telabis D Centruroides elegans insularis E Euphoria germinata F and G beetles of the family Elateridae H spider of the family Caponiidae I some individuals of lepidopterans." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520453" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

